 Army, 1933\u20131945 |date=1986\u20131987 |publisher=Bernard & Graefe |location=Koblenz |isbn=978-3-7637-5830-2}}\n* {{cite book |last=Hooton |first=E.R. |year=2007 |title=Luftwaffe at War: Gathering Storm 1933\u20131939 |volume=I |location=London |publisher=Chevron/Ian Allan |isbn=978-1-903223-71-0 |url-access=registration |url=https://archive.org/details/gatheringstorm190001hoot }}\n* {{cite book| last1 = Jentz| first1 = Thomas| title = Panzertruppen: The Complete Guide to the Creation & Combat Employment of Germany's Tank Force 1933\u20131942 (v. 1)| publisher = Schiffer | location = Atglen| year = 1996| isbn = 978-0887409158| ref = harv}}\n* {{cite book |last=Kennedy |first=Robert M. |title=The German Campaign in Poland (1939) |publisher=Zenger |year=1980 |isbn=978-0-89201-064-6}}\n* {{cite book |authorlink=Tony Kushner |last1=Kushner |first1=Tony |last2=Knox |first2=Katharine |year=1999 |url=https://books.google.com/?id=4iehSAirzqQC&pg=PA219&lpg=PA219&dq=Soviet+genocide+Poland |title=Refugees in an Age of Genocide |location=London, New York |publisher=[[Routledge]] |isbn=978-0-7146-4783-8 |accessdate=2 November 2011}}\n* {{cite book |authorlink=Richard C. Lukas |last=Lukas |first=Richard C. |title=Forgotten Holocaust: The Poles Under German Occupation, 1939\u20131944 |publisher=Hippocrene Books |year=2001 |isbn=978-0-7818-0901-6}}\n* {{cite book |last=Majer |first=Diemut |title=Non-Germans under the Third Reich: The Nazi Judicial and Administrative System in Germany and Occupied Eastern Europe, with Special Regard to Occupied Poland, 1939\u20131945 |publisher=Johns Hopkins University Press |year=2003 |isbn= 978-0-8018-6493-3|display-authors=et al.}}\n* {{cite press release |title=Nazi Loss in Poland Placed at 290,000 |work=The New York Times |date=28 September 1941 |url=https://select.nytimes.com/mem/archive/pdf?res=F50E11F63C5E1A7A93CAAB1782D85F458485F9 |accessdate=17 January 2009}}\n* {{cite book |authorlink=Anita J. Prazmowska |last=Prazmowska |first=Anita 