{"title_page": "Hody-Dobrovidka", "text_new": "{{Infobox settlement\n|official_name = Hody-Dobrovidka\n|native_name = \u0413\u043e\u0434\u0438-\u0414\u043e\u0431\u0440\u043e\u0432\u0456\u0434\u043a\u0430\n|image_skyline = File:\u0413\u043e\u0434\u0438-\u0414\u043e\u0431\u0440\u043e\u0432\u0456\u0434\u043a\u0430, \u0446\u0435\u0440\u043a\u0432\u0430.jpg\n|imagesize =\n|image_caption = The wooden church of St. George 1926\n|image_flag =\n|image_shield =\n|nickname =\n|motto =\n|image_map = \n|mapsize =\n|map_caption =\n|subdivision_type = Country\n|subdivision_name ={{UKR}}\n|subdivision_type1 = [[Oblasts of Ukraine|Province]]\n|subdivision_name1 ={{flag|Ivano-Frankivsk Oblast}}\n|subdivision_type2 = [[Raions of Ukraine|District]]\n|subdivision_name2 = [[File:Flag of Kolomyisky raion in Ivano-Frankivsk oblast.png|size|25px]] [[Kolomyia Raion]]\n|established_title =\n|established_date =\n|established_title1 =\n|established_date1 =\n|leader_title =\n|leader_name =\n|area_magnitude =\n|area_total_km2 = 12,88\n|area_water_km2 =\n|population_as_of =\n|population_note =\n|population_total = 967\n|population_metro =\n| population_density_km2 = auto\n|pushpin_map            = Ukraine Ivano-Frankivsk Oblast\n|pushpin_label_position =\n|pushpin_map_caption    = Ukraine Ivano-Frankivsk Oblast\n|pushpin_mapsize        =\n|coordinates      = {{coord|48|36|08|N|25|04|20|E|region:UA|display=inline,title}}\n|elevation_m = 335\n| timezone = EET\n| utc_offset = +2\n| timezone_DST = EEST\n| utc_offset_DST = +3\n| postal_code_type = [[Postal code]]\n|postal_code = 78244\n| area_code_type = [[Telephone numbering plan|Area code]]\n| area_code = +380 3433\n|blank_info =\n|blank1_info =\n|website = [http://1ua.com.ua/c22274  \u0441\u0435\u043b\u043e \u0413\u043e\u0434\u0438-\u0414\u043e\u0431\u0440\u043e\u0432\u0456\u0434\u043a\u0430 / \u0440\u0430\u0439\u0446\u0435\u043d\u0442\u0440 \u041a\u043e\u043b\u043e\u043c\u0438\u044f / \u043e\u0431\u043b\u0446\u0435\u043d\u0442\u0440 \u0406\u0432\u0430\u043d\u043e-\u0424\u0440\u0430\u043d\u043a\u0456\u0432\u0441\u044c\u043a] <sup>(Ukrainian)</sup>\n|footnotes =\n}}\n'''Hody-Dobrovidka''' ({{lang-uk|\u0413\u043e\u0301\u0434\u0438-\u0414\u043e\u0431\u0440\u043e\u0432\u0456\u0301\u0434\u043a\u0430}}) is a village in [[Kolomyia Raion]] of [[Ivano-Frankivsk Oblast]] in [[Western Ukraine]]. The population of the village is around 967 inhabitants, and local government is administered by Hodo-Dobrovidska village council.<ref>[http://rada.info/rada/04356774/ \u0413\u043e\u0434\u0438-\u0414\u043e\u0431\u0440\u043e\u0432\u0456\u0434\u0441\u044c\u043a\u0430 \u0441\u0456\u043b\u044c\u0441\u044c\u043a\u0430 \u0440\u0430\u0434\u0430] {{in lang|uk}}</ref>\n\n== Geography ==\nThe village is in a flat terrain on the altitude of {{convert|335|m|foot}} above sea level and area of the village totals is {{cvt|12.88|sqkm}}. It is at a distance {{convert|9|km|mi}} from the district center [[Kolomyia]] and {{convert|65|km|mi}} from the regional center of [[Ivano-Frankivsk]].\n\n== History and Attractions ==\nThe village was established in 1939 from the two separate villages, Hody and Dobrovidka.<ref>[[:uk:\u0413\u043e\u0434\u0438-\u0414\u043e\u0431\u0440\u043e\u0432\u0456\u0434\u043a\u0430|Hody-Dobrovidka]]</ref> The first written record about Dobrovidka dates back to 1451, and Gody village mentioned in 1857.<ref>[http://drymba.net/uk/1024960-selo-hody-dobrovidka \u0421\u0435\u043b\u043e \u0413\u043e\u0434\u0438-\u0414\u043e\u0431\u0440\u043e\u0432\u0456\u0434\u043a\u0430: \u043a\u0430\u0440\u0442\u0430 \u0432\u0443\u043b\u0438\u0446\u044c] {{in lang|uk}}</ref> The village has an architectural monument of local importance of Ivano-Frankivsk region. It is the Church of St. Dmitry 1923 (Wooden).<ref>[http://decerkva.org.ua/fra/hody-dobrovidka_dmytra.html \u0413\u043e\u0434\u0438-\u0414\u043e\u0431\u0440\u043e\u0432\u0456\u0434\u043a\u0430 \u0426\u0435\u0440\u043a\u0432\u0430 \u0421\u0432. \u0414\u043c\u0438\u0442\u0440\u0430 1923] {{in lang|uk}}</ref> The church belongs to the architectural monuments of local importance.<ref>[http://ukrainaincognita.com/ivano-frankivska-oblast/pamyatky-arkhitektury-mistsevogo-znachennya-ivano-frankivska-oblast-chastyn-0 \u041f\u0430\u043c'\u044f\u0442\u043a\u0438 \u0430\u0440\u0445\u0456\u0442\u0435\u043a\u0442\u0443\u0440\u0438 \u043c\u0456\u0441\u0446\u0435\u0432\u043e\u0433\u043e \u0437\u043d\u0430\u0447\u0435\u043d\u043d\u044f. \u0406\u0432\u0430\u043d\u043e-\u0424\u0440\u0430\u043d\u043a\u0456\u0432\u0441\u044c\u043a\u0430 \u043e\u0431\u043b\u0430\u0441\u0442\u044c. / \u0427\u0430\u0441\u0442\u0438\u043d\u0430 3 / 915, \u0426\u0435\u0440\u043a\u0432\u0430 \u0421\u0432. \u0414\u043c\u0438\u0442\u0440\u0456\u044f (\u0434\u0435\u0440.) 1852 \u0440. (N 801)] {{in lang|uk}}</ref> There are also the Church of St. George 1926 (Wooden).<ref>[http://decerkva.org.ua/fra/hody-dobrovidka_yuria.html \u0413\u043e\u0434\u0438-\u0414\u043e\u0431\u0440\u043e\u0432\u0456\u0434\u043a\u0430. \u0426\u0435\u0440\u043a\u0432\u0430 \u0421\u0432. \u042e\u0440\u0456\u044f 1926] {{in lang|uk}}</ref>\n\n== Famous people ==\n* '''Melnychuk Petro Dmytrovych'''<ref>\n*[http://ntsh.org/content/ganitkevich-yaroslav-ukrayinskiy-medichniy-kalendar-na-2013-rik \u0423\u043a\u0440\u0430\u0457\u043d\u0441\u044c\u043a\u0438\u0439 \u043c\u0435\u0434\u0438\u0447\u043d\u0438\u0439 \u043a\u0430\u043b\u0435\u043d\u0434\u0430\u0440 \u043d\u0430 2013 \u0440\u0456\u043a/1913, 14 \u043b\u0438\u043f\u043d\u044f \u2013 100 \u0440\u043e\u043a\u0456\u0432] {{in lang|uk}}\n*http://mistaua.com/\u041f\u043e\u0441\u0442\u0430\u0442\u0456/\u0412\u0447\u0435\u043d\u0456/\u043c\u0435\u043b\u044c\u043d\u0438\u0447\u0443\u043a-\u043f\u0435\u0442\u0440\u043e-\u0434\u043c\u0438\u0442\u0440\u043e\u0432\u0438\u0447/1551/?setcity=2304 {{in lang|uk}}</ref> (1913-2004) &ndash; Candidate of Pharmaceutical Sciences, Associate Professor, Deputy Director for Science of Lviv State Medical Institute (1944-1961), known phytotherapeutist. He graduated from the [[Lviv University]] (1939), was twice sentenced to death, once by the [[Soviet annexation of Eastern Galicia, Volhynia and Northern Bukovina|Bolsheviks]] (1941) and once by the [[German-occupied Europe |German occupiers]] (1944).\n\n== References ==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n== External links ==\n* [http://atu.minregion.gov.ua/en/ustriy_page/5098 Hodo-Dobrovidska village council]\n* [http://weather.in.ua/en/ivano-frankovskaja/5324 weather.in.ua/Hody-Dobrovidka]\n\n{{Ivano-Frankivsk Oblast}}\n\n[[Category:Villages in Ivano-Frankivsk Oblast]]\n\n{{IvanoFrankivsk-geo-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox settlement\n|official_name = Hody-Dobrovidka\n|native_name = \u0413\u043e\u0434\u0438-\u0414\u043e\u0431\u0440\u043e\u0432\u0456\u0434\u043a\u0430\n|image_skyline = File:\u0413\u043e\u0434\u0438-\u0414\u043e\u0431\u0440\u043e\u0432\u0456\u0434\u043a\u0430, \u0446\u0435\u0440\u043a\u0432\u0430.jpg\n|imagesize =\n|image_caption = The wooden church of St. George 1926\n|image_flag =\n|image_shield =\n|nickname =\n|motto =\n|image_map = \n|mapsize =\n|map_caption =\n|subdivision_type = Country\n|subdivision_name ={{UKR}}\n|subdivision_type1 = [[Oblasts of Ukraine|Province]]\n|subdivision_name1 ={{flag|Ivano-Frankivsk Oblast}}\n|subdivision_type2 = [[Raions of Ukraine|District]]\n|subdivision_name2 = [[File:Flag of Kolomyisky raion in Ivano-Frankivsk oblast.png|size|25px]] [[Kolomyia Raion]]\n|established_title =\n|established_date =\n|established_title1 =\n|established_date1 =\n|leader_title =\n|leader_name =\n|area_magnitude =\n|area_total_km2 = 12,88\n|area_water_km2 =\n|population_as_of =\n|population_note =\n|population_total = 967\n|population_metro =\n| population_density_km2 = auto\n|pushpin_map            = Ukraine Ivano-Frankivsk Oblast\n|pushpin_label_position =\n|pushpin_map_caption    = Ukraine Ivano-Frankivsk Oblast\n|pushpin_mapsize        =\n|coordinates      = {{coord|48|36|08|N|25|04|20|E|region:UA|display=inline,title}}\n|elevation_m = 335\n| 